代码：
Java：
```
class Solution {
    public List<Integer> addToArrayForm(int[] num, int k) {
        /* Set up */
        int n = num.length;
        int cur = k;
        List<Integer> res = new ArrayList();
        
        /* run the addition backwards digit by digit*/
        int i = n;
        while (--i >= 0|| cur > 0){
        /* Adding a new digit*/
            if (i >= 0){
                cur += num[i];
            }
        /* Carry addition simulator*/
            res.add(cur % 10);
            cur = cur / 10;;
        }
        /* return the result reversely since we adding up reversely*/
        Collections.reverse(res);
        return res;
    }
}
```

Scala:
```
object Solution {
    def addToArrayForm(num: Array[Int], K: Int): List[Int] = {
        // Set up
        var res = List[Int]()
        var k = K
        
        // Reverse the num list, and initialize the carry
        // Scala variable definition 101
        // carry is repeatedly folding out and most addition is taken care here
        val carry = num.reverse.foldLeft(0)((sum, x)=>{
          val temp = k % 10 + x + sum
          k = k / 10
          res :::= List(temp % 10)
          temp / 10}
        )
        // edge case when there is k or carry left
        if(k == 0){
          if (carry == 1) res :::= List(1)
          res
        }
        else{
          k = k + carry
          while(k > 0){
            res :::= List(k % 10)
            k  = k / 10
          }
          res
        }
    }
}
```

复杂度：
TC: O(n + k)
SC: O(n + k)

