思路：字符串 s 中的两个 c 之间用双指针法算距离，第一个 c 和最后一个 c 直接循环计算
---
```java
class Solution {
    public int[] shortestToChar(String s, char c) {
        // 1. 统计 c 的个数并且将 c 对应的值置为0
        char[] chs = s.toCharArray();
        int length = chs.length;
        int[] res = new int[length];
        List<Integer> boundaries = new ArrayList<>();
        for (int i = 0; i < length; i++) {
            if (chs[i] == c) {
                res[i] = 0;
                boundaries.add(i);
            } else {
                res[i] = -1;
            }
        }
        if (boundaries.isEmpty()) return res;
        // 2. 值为0的下标，两两一对，利用双指针法将其范围内的值置为离其最近的举例
        for (int i = 1; i < boundaries.size(); i++) {
            getShortestDistance(res, boundaries.get(i - 1), boundaries.get(i));
        }
        // 3. 处理第一个0和最后一个0
        int first = boundaries.get(0);
        int value = 0;
        while (first >= 0) {
            res[first--] = value++;
        }

        int last = boundaries.get(boundaries.size() - 1);
        value = 0;
        while (last < length) {
            res[last++] = value++;
        }

        return res;
    }

    // 计算数组在 [start,end] 范围内举例边界较短的举例
    private void getShortestDistance(int[] nums, int start, int end) {
        int value = 0;
        while (start < end) {
            nums[start++] = value;
            nums[end--] = value;
            value++;
        }
        if (start == end) nums[start] = value;
    }
}
```
---
- Time: O(2N)
- Space: O(N)

