### 思路

从左到右，然后从右到左遍历两遍
找到C并记录它和S[i]的距离，最后取最小值

### 代码


```java
class Solution {
    public int[] shortestToChar(String s, char c) {
        int[] res = new int[s.length()]; // create new array to store answer
        int dummy = Integer.MIN_VALUE/2; // initiate a variable as the min value to store char c
                                         // /2 to avoid index out of bound

        for(int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++){ // from left to right
            if(s.charAt(i) == c) dummy = i;  // find first c, store it and calculate the next number 
            res[i] = i - dummy;
        }

        dummy = Integer.MAX_VALUE;            // from right to left
        for(int i = s.length() - 1; i >= 0; i--){ 
            if(s.charAt(i) == c) dummy = i;
            res[i] = Math.min(res[i], dummy - i);  // compare to find the min and store it
        }
        return res;

    }
}

```

**复杂度分析**
- 时间复杂度：O(N)，其中 N 为数组长度。
- 空间复杂度：O(N)

